WEBVTT

01:43.190 --> 01:45.960
[Love Song in Winter]

01:46.120 --> 01:49.080
[Episode 5]

01:50.880 --> 01:51.880
I remember the first time

01:51.910 --> 01:52.950
I saw you.

01:53.740 --> 01:55.170
You were running on the court,

01:57.090 --> 01:58.009
and I couldn't help but think,

01:58.950 --> 01:59.430
how could someone

01:59.470 --> 02:00.870
run so badly?

02:02.590 --> 02:03.690
It was truly awful.

02:12.690 --> 02:13.660
Yan.

02:13.980 --> 02:15.050
Are you okay?

02:15.420 --> 02:16.220
I'm so tired.

02:16.250 --> 02:17.660
Just go ahead and run; don't mind me.

02:17.720 --> 02:18.690
Are you exhausted?

02:19.200 --> 02:19.860
No way.

02:20.560 --> 02:22.100
Hurry up.

02:27.150 --> 02:27.630
Yan.

02:27.650 --> 02:29.200
Why do you look like a zombie?

02:29.810 --> 02:30.470
Do I?

02:30.870 --> 02:31.690
I don't think so.

02:39.710 --> 02:40.310
Awesome.

02:40.329 --> 02:41.110
Not bad.

02:46.620 --> 02:47.630
I can't keep going.

02:47.710 --> 02:48.590
I really can't.

02:48.590 --> 02:49.450
What's wrong with you?

02:49.590 --> 02:50.150
Yan.

02:50.150 --> 02:51.410
There were two game-winning plays today.

02:52.390 --> 02:53.020
Are you okay?

02:53.310 --> 02:53.790
What's wrong?

02:53.790 --> 02:54.410
Excuse me,

02:54.470 --> 02:54.950
young lady.

02:55.030 --> 02:56.310
You can't sit down right away after a long run.

02:56.350 --> 02:57.200
Get up quickly.

02:57.470 --> 02:58.430
It's fine, sir.

02:58.450 --> 02:59.500
She only ran one lap.

02:59.950 --> 03:00.990
Have a little respect for me.

03:02.670 --> 03:04.440
I was just tying my shoelaces.

03:04.780 --> 03:05.730
Only one lap?

03:06.710 --> 03:07.750
Finish tying them quickly and keep running.

03:10.190 --> 03:11.790
Come on, just one more lap.

03:12.270 --> 03:12.870
Let's go.

03:13.710 --> 03:14.410
I'll help you up.

03:15.900 --> 03:16.810
My girlfriend.

03:17.190 --> 03:18.020
Which one?

03:18.430 --> 03:19.490
The one in purple.

03:19.680 --> 03:21.150
They're all wearing purple.

03:22.190 --> 03:22.990
Hang in there.

03:37.910 --> 03:39.310
Actually, back in high school,

03:39.620 --> 03:40.820
I wanted to apply to the police academy.

03:41.829 --> 03:43.230
But my parents didn't agree,

03:43.960 --> 03:45.390
so I went to Ninghai University

03:45.390 --> 03:46.190
to study engineering instead.

03:47.750 --> 03:48.760
But I'm not interested

03:48.800 --> 03:49.710
in engineering.

03:50.280 --> 03:51.450
Every day feels like a struggle,

03:51.550 --> 03:52.770
just going through the motions,

03:52.910 --> 03:53.510
trying to get by.

03:54.490 --> 03:55.470
Until one day,

03:56.030 --> 03:58.210
I found out you were going after a thief.

04:01.310 --> 04:02.990
Someone who threw up after running just one lap

04:03.030 --> 04:04.820
around the basketball court was about to catch a thief.

04:05.750 --> 04:06.550
How brave...

04:07.630 --> 04:08.830
is that!

04:10.070 --> 04:11.150
How

04:11.150 --> 04:12.230
utterly overconfident!

04:18.870 --> 04:20.110
Are you praising me?

04:21.760 --> 04:22.760
Kind of.

04:25.990 --> 04:27.740
I've bought the beef noodles.

04:27.860 --> 04:28.550
Anything else?

04:28.630 --> 04:29.640
Thanks, bro.

04:29.870 --> 04:31.510
I'll be your servant when you come back.

04:31.670 --> 04:32.750
Wait, just make sure

04:32.750 --> 04:33.610
you hold on tight on your way back.

04:33.710 --> 04:34.230
Don't spill it.

04:34.230 --> 04:35.070
I know.

04:35.070 --> 04:36.150
That soup is the essence.

04:36.350 --> 04:37.060
Move aside!

04:38.030 --> 04:38.909
Catch the thief!

04:39.390 --> 04:40.070
Thief!

04:43.830 --> 04:44.570
Move aside!

04:46.440 --> 04:47.120
Stop there!

04:53.980 --> 04:54.560
Stop there!

05:13.790 --> 05:14.370
Move aside!

05:18.660 --> 05:19.370
Move aside!

05:25.030 --> 05:26.080
Give me the bag!

05:27.740 --> 05:28.360
Go away!

05:35.600 --> 05:36.290
Go away!

05:36.850 --> 05:37.560
Go away!

05:41.090 --> 05:41.820
Go away!

05:42.550 --> 05:43.180
Go away!

05:49.320 --> 05:49.950
Handcuff him.

05:49.970 --> 05:51.480
Come on, let me handle it.

05:51.920 --> 05:52.560
It's him.

05:52.590 --> 05:53.840
He's the one who stole my bag.

05:53.909 --> 05:54.470
Check

05:54.490 --> 05:55.510
if anything's missing.

05:56.620 --> 05:57.480
Nothing's missing.

05:57.700 --> 05:58.890
Thank you, officer.

05:59.310 --> 06:00.200
Thank you both.

06:00.230 --> 06:00.990
You're welcome.

06:01.760 --> 06:02.490
Take him in.

06:07.180 --> 06:08.430
Is it not your bag?

06:08.990 --> 06:09.850
No.

06:09.920 --> 06:11.300
I thought it was your bag.

06:11.320 --> 06:12.670
You're being a good Samaritan, huh?

06:15.150 --> 06:16.150
Quite brave.

06:18.300 --> 06:19.390
I'm Jiang Chengyi.

06:20.030 --> 06:20.790
My name is...

06:21.430 --> 06:22.070
I'm…

06:24.080 --> 06:25.170
Sorry,

06:26.610 --> 06:27.980
I'm really out of shape.

06:28.000 --> 06:28.870
I know.

06:29.120 --> 06:30.150
You ran a lap around the basketball court

06:30.150 --> 06:31.550
and collapsed, didn't you?

06:31.590 --> 06:33.230
Today, you've really outdone yourself.

06:34.110 --> 06:35.550
How do you know?

06:35.650 --> 06:36.909
I was playing basketball that day.

06:39.110 --> 06:40.510
Are we from the same school?

06:40.550 --> 06:40.990
Yes.

06:41.010 --> 06:41.670
I thought

06:41.670 --> 06:43.270
you were from the police academy next door.

06:43.430 --> 06:44.700
I don't look like someone from the police academy at all.

06:45.120 --> 06:46.550
But that move you made earlier,

06:46.920 --> 06:47.830
it really

06:47.909 --> 06:48.909
looked like it—

06:48.930 --> 06:50.000
like a real cop.

06:50.370 --> 06:51.290
Thank you.

06:52.310 --> 06:52.750
Well...

06:53.420 --> 06:54.300
Thank you.

06:54.630 --> 06:55.480
You're welcome.

06:57.110 --> 06:57.710
I'm leaving.

07:05.720 --> 07:06.840
What's your name?

07:09.160 --> 07:11.420
I'm... I'm Lu Yan.

07:11.920 --> 07:13.470
I major in Anesthesiology, Class of '14.

07:23.550 --> 07:25.790
Solid or liquid...

07:27.190 --> 07:30.110
Solid or liquid...

07:31.520 --> 07:33.230
Solid or liquid...

07:33.590 --> 07:34.150
Entering...

07:35.390 --> 07:36.310
Entering...

07:36.330 --> 07:37.730
Solid and liquid

07:37.830 --> 07:38.870
substances...

07:39.510 --> 07:40.630
Solid or...

07:41.190 --> 07:43.370
Solid or...

07:44.070 --> 07:45.830
Solid or liquid...

07:46.030 --> 07:48.030
Solid or...

07:48.750 --> 07:50.560
Substances entering the lower respiratory tract...

07:50.620 --> 07:52.430
Solid or...

07:52.510 --> 07:54.080
Solid...

07:54.110 --> 07:55.870
Solid or liquid...

07:56.150 --> 07:57.909
Solid or liquid...

08:06.380 --> 08:08.500
From that day on, I realized

08:10.710 --> 08:12.490
I shouldn't keep drifting along like this.

08:13.540 --> 08:14.990
Even though I hadn't joined the police academy yet,

08:15.790 --> 08:16.870
I was already

08:16.870 --> 08:18.390
holding myself

08:18.630 --> 08:19.670
to a police officer's standard.

08:20.510 --> 08:22.390
So every day, I would go to the playground

08:22.410 --> 08:23.340
for physical training.

08:26.020 --> 08:28.110
No wonder, back then,

08:28.110 --> 08:29.270
I could see you every morning

08:29.300 --> 08:30.690
running laps on the playground.

08:33.240 --> 08:34.299
I ran

08:34.630 --> 08:35.429
ten laps,

08:36.710 --> 08:38.350
and you were still memorizing the same passage.

08:40.049 --> 08:40.960
I...

08:41.440 --> 08:44.220
I really wasn't good at memorizing

08:44.260 --> 08:45.390
back then.

08:45.860 --> 08:47.220
I ran for a whole week,

08:47.870 --> 08:49.520
and you still hadn't finished the first chapter.

08:50.460 --> 08:51.390
That's enough.

08:53.910 --> 08:55.640
Later, after a semester,

08:56.900 --> 08:58.160
my fitness level met the standard.

09:00.190 --> 09:01.720
You failed your course, right?

09:03.600 --> 09:04.580
Don't bring it up.

09:05.580 --> 09:06.610
Did you retake the exam?

09:06.640 --> 09:07.470
Jiang Chengyi.

09:28.950 --> 09:29.940
You're off work now, right?

09:32.270 --> 09:33.480
Let me take you home.

09:38.330 --> 09:41.700
[Huiting Complex]

09:49.920 --> 09:50.450
Senior.

09:50.470 --> 09:51.310
Qin Yue.

09:51.380 --> 09:52.200
Is it done?

09:53.590 --> 09:54.210
Yes.

09:54.240 --> 09:55.240
Scan the QR code,

09:55.240 --> 09:56.030
and you can use it once you're connected.

09:56.590 --> 09:57.050
Okay.

09:57.420 --> 09:59.290
This is my junior, Qin Yue.

09:59.390 --> 10:00.190
He's also a criminal police officer

10:00.190 --> 10:01.470
from Anshan District.

10:02.390 --> 10:02.880
Lei Yiming,

10:02.910 --> 10:03.560
from our criminal police team.

10:03.590 --> 10:04.070
Hello, Senior.

10:04.070 --> 10:04.510
Hello.

10:05.150 --> 10:06.540
I asked them to help

10:06.570 --> 10:08.040
install a video doorbell for you.

10:08.280 --> 10:09.380
Go back and scan the QR code.

10:09.400 --> 10:11.300
After downloading the app

10:11.510 --> 10:12.990
and connecting it to your home Wi-Fi,

10:13.000 --> 10:13.560
it will be ready to use.

10:13.590 --> 10:14.870
Anyone who passes by

10:14.930 --> 10:16.130
or lingers outside your door will be recorded.

10:17.620 --> 10:18.380
Thank you.

10:25.270 --> 10:26.650
This is Dr. Lu

10:26.670 --> 10:28.480
from People's Hospital.

10:30.570 --> 10:31.460
Hello, Dr. Lu.

10:31.990 --> 10:32.520
Dr. Lu.

10:32.690 --> 10:33.150
Senior.

10:33.190 --> 10:34.510
Did you two know each other before,

10:34.540 --> 10:35.900
or just meet recently?

10:36.680 --> 10:37.780
We...

10:38.460 --> 10:39.810
We are

10:40.550 --> 10:41.560
university classmates.

10:43.450 --> 10:44.500
University classmates?

10:45.900 --> 10:47.320
Glad to hear that.

10:47.350 --> 10:48.200
This afternoon,

10:48.200 --> 10:49.430
we happened to finish our work and had nothing to do,

10:49.460 --> 10:50.310
so we came to help our senior's classmate

10:50.350 --> 10:51.380
with the installation.

10:51.790 --> 10:52.790
If nothing else, just get in the car.

10:52.830 --> 10:53.710
I'll drop you off later.

10:53.790 --> 10:54.860
You're giving us a ride today?

10:55.250 --> 10:55.710
Okay.

10:55.750 --> 10:56.110
Thank you, Senior.

10:56.110 --> 10:56.960
Goodbye, Dr. Lu.

11:01.270 --> 11:02.800
It's fine, just let him help out.

11:02.970 --> 11:04.110
Now that it's installed,

11:04.130 --> 11:05.290
you don't have to worry about it anymore.

11:05.640 --> 11:06.630
You can just go home

11:07.020 --> 11:07.910
and get a good night's sleep.

11:09.880 --> 11:10.690
Thank you.

11:11.780 --> 11:12.740
Well,

11:13.670 --> 11:14.690
I'll head up first.

11:14.790 --> 11:15.270
Okay.

11:15.310 --> 11:16.950
If you have any questions,

11:17.450 --> 11:18.080
just reach out to me.

11:19.660 --> 11:20.230
Bye.

11:20.510 --> 11:20.950
Bye.

11:42.130 --> 11:43.400
Do you have any manners?

11:46.000 --> 11:49.210
[Outpatient]

11:51.440 --> 11:56.130
[Nurse Station]

12:02.270 --> 12:03.540
Hello.

12:03.570 --> 12:04.380
Your delivery has arrived.

12:04.430 --> 12:05.560
Please come down and pick it up.

12:06.100 --> 12:08.160
I didn't order anything.

12:08.670 --> 12:10.390
It's from Mr. Zhang.

12:10.430 --> 12:11.510
He insisted that

12:11.510 --> 12:12.740
I hand it to you personally.

12:14.170 --> 12:14.710
Okay.

12:14.740 --> 12:15.710
Please wait for a moment.

12:17.110 --> 12:24.700
[Department of Anesthesiology]

12:19.210 --> 12:20.620
Can you keep an eye on things for me?

12:20.620 --> 12:21.270
I'm stepping out for a bit.

12:21.290 --> 12:21.910
Okay.

12:25.660 --> 12:26.190
Here.

12:27.950 --> 12:28.670
Thank you.

12:28.710 --> 12:29.350
Sorry to trouble you.

12:29.350 --> 12:29.990
Never mind.

12:33.370 --> 12:35.420
[Privacy Protection: The customer's address is hidden.
You can log into the delivery or rider app to view it]

12:50.510 --> 12:51.400
Zhang Xiaohui.

12:53.570 --> 12:54.930
Zhang Xiaohui, what are you doing?

12:55.270 --> 12:56.250
Surprise!

12:56.540 --> 12:57.340
Come over here.

12:57.500 --> 12:58.330
Give me a hug.

12:59.240 --> 13:00.380
What do you mean?

13:00.780 --> 13:02.120
Why didn't you bring it yourself?

13:02.150 --> 13:03.260
Why did you have to order takeout?

13:03.290 --> 13:04.580
This takeout

13:04.790 --> 13:06.280
really needed to be delivered by the delivery person

13:06.310 --> 13:06.790
because...

13:06.810 --> 13:07.750
Are you starting

13:07.750 --> 13:08.630
to doubt me again?

13:08.650 --> 13:09.350
Do you think

13:09.350 --> 13:10.270
I'm not on duty

13:10.290 --> 13:11.710
and meeting up with another man?

13:11.750 --> 13:12.350
No.

13:12.350 --> 13:13.510
How could I not trust you?

13:13.600 --> 13:14.310
I just saw,

13:14.350 --> 13:15.410
there was no guy here.

13:15.640 --> 13:16.710
What do you want me to do

13:16.710 --> 13:17.590
for you to leave me alone?

13:17.620 --> 13:19.150
Honey, it's my fault.

13:19.150 --> 13:20.390
I won't doubt you again,

13:20.390 --> 13:20.920
okay?

13:20.970 --> 13:22.200
As long as you're not working anymore.

13:23.510 --> 13:24.180
What?

13:25.440 --> 13:26.830
Do you think that's possible?

13:26.860 --> 13:28.030
Even if I stayed home every day

13:28.030 --> 13:29.150
as a housewife,

13:29.390 --> 13:30.230
you'd still doubt

13:30.250 --> 13:31.200
that I was doing something else

13:31.240 --> 13:32.400
when you were out working.

13:33.420 --> 13:34.980
If you're willing to marry me,

13:35.830 --> 13:37.420
I'd be willing to quit my job for you.

13:37.590 --> 13:38.620
Zhang Xiaohui,

13:38.620 --> 13:39.440
can you understand human language?

13:39.770 --> 13:40.700
Your jealousy

13:40.750 --> 13:41.910
isn't my problem.

13:41.990 --> 13:43.150
And I definitely

13:43.180 --> 13:44.390
won't give up my job for you.

13:44.630 --> 13:45.640
Qianqian, you can do it.

13:45.670 --> 13:46.830
Didn't you say you love me?

13:46.870 --> 13:47.290
Right?

13:47.340 --> 13:48.000
Let go of me!

13:48.470 --> 13:49.540
I'm sorry.

13:50.400 --> 13:51.600
Don't leave me.

13:51.670 --> 13:52.830
I really can't live without you.

13:52.830 --> 13:53.510
I'm sorry.

13:53.630 --> 13:54.750
Zhang Xiaohui, this is the hospital.

13:54.790 --> 13:55.670
Let go of me.

13:55.870 --> 13:56.820
Don't leave me.

13:57.080 --> 13:57.720
If you don't let go,

13:57.720 --> 13:58.820
I'll break up with you.

13:59.200 --> 13:59.910
What did you say?

14:00.010 --> 14:01.160
I said, "Break up."

14:04.150 --> 14:05.040
Break up?

14:05.910 --> 14:08.010
Why does everyone keep saying "break up"?

14:08.190 --> 14:09.340
Tell me!

14:09.910 --> 14:10.910
Why?

14:12.110 --> 14:13.480
Why?

14:14.350 --> 14:15.260
Why are you here so early?

14:15.360 --> 14:15.890
Sir.

14:16.000 --> 14:16.460
Good morning.

14:16.480 --> 14:16.920
Good morning.

14:20.080 --> 14:21.520
Just tell me!

14:22.850 --> 14:24.250
Tell me.

14:24.550 --> 14:25.590
Tell me!

14:25.590 --> 14:27.070
What are you doing, Zhang Xiaohui?

14:28.870 --> 14:29.590
Nothing.

14:29.610 --> 14:30.820
I got takeout for her.

14:32.640 --> 14:33.820
You'd better leave now.

14:34.030 --> 14:34.790
If you don't,

14:34.810 --> 14:35.900
I'll call security.

14:35.990 --> 14:36.670
Don't call security.

14:36.690 --> 14:37.430
Don't.

14:37.670 --> 14:38.400
Security.

14:38.420 --> 14:39.410
Security!

14:40.590 --> 14:42.000
Just you wait.

14:42.980 --> 14:43.670
I'm leaving.

14:43.750 --> 14:45.100
I'm leaving.

14:45.310 --> 14:45.840
Bye.

14:45.920 --> 14:46.530
Be careful.

14:46.950 --> 14:47.830
I'm sorry.

14:48.110 --> 14:49.030
Crazy.

14:52.590 --> 14:53.270
Are you okay?

15:00.810 --> 15:03.700
[Ninghai Anshan People's Hospital]

15:16.810 --> 15:17.840
Still upset?

15:21.560 --> 15:23.040
Don't dwell on it so much.

15:24.570 --> 15:26.120
Does Zhang Xiaohui always act like this?

15:27.830 --> 15:29.180
He's not usually like this.

15:30.130 --> 15:30.830
He used to be

15:30.870 --> 15:31.980
completely obedient to me.

15:32.110 --> 15:32.830
You know what?

15:33.630 --> 15:35.210
Every day, the meals I brought with me

15:35.710 --> 15:36.760
were made by him,

15:36.790 --> 15:37.630
getting up at 5 AM

15:37.670 --> 15:38.750
just to cook for me.

15:40.510 --> 15:41.320
Are you stupid?

15:41.350 --> 15:42.870
What's so special about him making you a meal?

15:42.950 --> 15:43.590
Isn't the food at the hospital

15:43.630 --> 15:45.040
better than what he cooks?

15:47.870 --> 15:48.680
Fine.

15:49.390 --> 15:50.230
Go on.

15:52.250 --> 15:53.660
A few months ago,

15:55.010 --> 15:56.350
a few of my high school classmates

15:56.350 --> 15:57.190
came to visit me.

15:57.570 --> 15:59.510
We were chatting and having so much fun

15:59.720 --> 16:00.630
when he called me.

16:00.670 --> 16:01.590
I didn't pick up,

16:02.030 --> 16:03.920
and then he suddenly got really angry

16:04.410 --> 16:06.140
and smashed everything in the house.

16:07.190 --> 16:07.670
Wait.

16:07.700 --> 16:09.340
Why didn't you tell me?

16:11.990 --> 16:13.400
I thought

16:14.350 --> 16:15.870
it was just an argument.

16:17.370 --> 16:18.670
Later, I found out

16:19.260 --> 16:20.720
it was because his ex-girlfriend

16:20.870 --> 16:21.690
cheated on him.

16:22.390 --> 16:23.190
That's why

16:23.210 --> 16:24.450
he feels insecure now.

16:24.980 --> 16:25.950
Do you remember

16:25.950 --> 16:27.070
the slip dress

16:27.230 --> 16:28.370
you gave me?

16:28.800 --> 16:30.200
He threw it away.

16:31.140 --> 16:31.840
Qianqian,

16:32.830 --> 16:33.350
listen.

16:33.390 --> 16:34.790
He's in a very dangerous state right now.

16:34.810 --> 16:35.790
He could easily

16:35.830 --> 16:37.110
do something extreme.

16:37.430 --> 16:38.390
You have to break up with him.

16:38.430 --> 16:39.230
I'm not joking.

16:39.270 --> 16:39.640
Do you understand?

16:39.670 --> 16:40.510
I understand.

16:40.530 --> 16:41.390
I actually wanted to

16:41.430 --> 16:42.350
break up with him a long time ago.

16:43.120 --> 16:43.740
But,

16:44.550 --> 16:46.580
he knows where I work

16:46.710 --> 16:48.410
and where my parents live.

16:48.440 --> 16:49.750
I'm so scared that

16:49.770 --> 16:50.970
if he gets emotional,

16:51.190 --> 16:52.110
he'll show up at my door.

16:52.150 --> 16:53.270
Then, you should talk to a police officer.

16:53.300 --> 16:54.480
Ask for advice,

16:54.510 --> 16:55.630
or get some sort of

16:55.660 --> 16:57.270
personal safety protection order.

17:03.020 --> 17:05.109
Captain Jiang is a police officer, isn't he?

17:05.390 --> 17:06.589
Could you ask him for me?

17:08.349 --> 17:08.869
I...

17:10.410 --> 17:11.349
He...

17:12.869 --> 17:14.510
Go ask him yourself.

17:15.119 --> 17:17.050
After all, I don't know much

17:17.079 --> 17:19.079
about what's going on between you two.

17:19.440 --> 17:20.310
He's a really nice person;

17:20.349 --> 17:21.589
you can ask him anything.

17:22.190 --> 17:23.109
How do you know?

17:24.349 --> 17:25.030
I...

17:27.630 --> 17:28.550
Just read it from his expression.

17:29.700 --> 17:31.450
I'm going to prepare for the surgery now.

17:31.470 --> 17:32.900
Let's grab something tasty tonight.

17:33.880 --> 17:35.270
Could you stay with me a little longer?

17:36.210 --> 17:37.140
Just one more minute,

17:37.270 --> 17:38.030
okay?

17:40.340 --> 17:41.800
Can you help me open it?

17:41.820 --> 17:42.800
I can't do it.

17:50.530 --> 17:51.720
Wen,

17:52.010 --> 17:53.120
how about the autograph

17:53.150 --> 17:54.430
I asked you

17:54.450 --> 17:55.100
to help me get last time?

17:56.530 --> 17:57.520
The autograph?

17:58.860 --> 18:00.000
Oh, do you have time tonight?

18:00.410 --> 18:01.390
Tonight?

18:01.790 --> 18:03.980
Are you meeting Dr. Han?

18:05.270 --> 18:06.400
It's a surprise.

18:08.550 --> 18:09.550
A surprise?

18:11.390 --> 18:12.740
Really?

18:13.030 --> 18:13.790
That's great!

18:13.810 --> 18:14.320
Alright then,

18:14.350 --> 18:15.950
Wen, see you tonight.

18:16.240 --> 18:17.530
Let me know when you're off work,

18:17.550 --> 18:18.370
and I'll come pick you up.

18:18.630 --> 18:19.190
Sure.

18:26.750 --> 18:27.420
Well,

18:27.630 --> 18:28.510
Captain Jiang,

18:28.710 --> 18:29.830
what should I do

18:29.850 --> 18:30.960
about my situation now?

18:33.230 --> 18:34.120
For this kind of matter,

18:34.150 --> 18:35.670
honestly, I'd still suggest you

18:36.100 --> 18:37.340
call the police first.

18:37.670 --> 18:38.910
But if you're really worried that

18:38.990 --> 18:40.430
calling the police might provoke him,

18:41.310 --> 18:42.710
try to choose

18:42.730 --> 18:43.890
a crowded place

18:44.310 --> 18:45.470
to talk about breaking up.

18:45.760 --> 18:46.730
A public place—

18:46.840 --> 18:49.050
like a busy intersection

18:49.070 --> 18:50.490
with traffic police around.

18:51.380 --> 18:52.850
That way,

18:53.030 --> 18:54.150
if there's any danger,

18:54.740 --> 18:55.320
someone can step in

18:55.350 --> 18:56.430
to protect you right away.

18:58.950 --> 18:59.510
How about this?

18:59.580 --> 19:01.270
I'll give you my junior's phone number.

19:01.290 --> 19:02.590
He happens to be

19:02.590 --> 19:03.340
at the Anshan Police Station.

19:03.440 --> 19:04.310
If you need anything,

19:04.550 --> 19:05.850
you can contact him right away.

19:10.470 --> 19:11.390
You're still living

19:11.390 --> 19:12.070
with your boyfriend, right?

19:12.640 --> 19:13.150
Yes.

19:13.560 --> 19:14.370
We are

19:14.470 --> 19:15.770
renting a place together.

19:16.020 --> 19:17.670
When you go back to pack your things,

19:18.030 --> 19:18.860
take someone with you.

19:18.990 --> 19:19.580
Alright,

19:20.070 --> 19:22.820
I'll ask Lu Yan to go with me.

19:23.770 --> 19:24.510
I'll also leave you

19:24.510 --> 19:25.030
my number.

19:25.330 --> 19:26.490
If you need anything,

19:26.950 --> 19:27.960
you can contact me too.

19:28.820 --> 19:29.510
Really?

19:29.510 --> 19:29.960
Yes.

19:30.240 --> 19:30.750
Captain Jiang,

19:30.790 --> 19:31.950
you're such a good person.

19:32.110 --> 19:33.150
I think

19:33.180 --> 19:34.710
whoever becomes your girlfriend

19:34.090 --> 19:34.910
[Edit Contact] [Jiang Cheng]

19:34.790 --> 19:36.190
will really be lucky.

19:34.910 --> 19:36.250
[Refuse] [Answer]

19:34.910 --> 19:36.250
[Lu Yan]

19:38.600 --> 19:39.390
Phone call.

19:39.410 --> 19:40.260
Sorry.

19:42.110 --> 19:43.480
Hello, Yan. What's up?

19:43.720 --> 19:44.440
Qianqian,

19:45.310 --> 19:46.560
do you

19:46.590 --> 19:47.590
have plans tonight?

19:48.300 --> 19:49.150
Where are we going?

19:49.720 --> 19:51.310
Come with me to a place tonight.

19:52.060 --> 19:52.670
What's it for?

19:52.670 --> 19:54.090
If you don't explain it clearly, I'm not going.

19:56.560 --> 19:57.970
Come with me...

19:58.000 --> 19:59.160
Come with me on a date.

19:59.900 --> 20:01.370
Go on a date with you?

20:02.350 --> 20:03.390
Sure!

20:03.430 --> 20:04.410
Which one?

20:04.440 --> 20:05.600
Is it the 185 guy?

20:05.630 --> 20:06.950
Or the Leo?

20:06.980 --> 20:07.600
Or the one

20:07.630 --> 20:08.620
who does rock climbing?

20:08.910 --> 20:09.510
Alright.

20:09.580 --> 20:10.150
You...

20:10.180 --> 20:11.530
You have the password to my house, don't you?

20:11.600 --> 20:12.540
Go change into

20:12.540 --> 20:13.350
a nice outfit first.

20:13.410 --> 20:15.060
Dress up beautifully.

20:15.100 --> 20:16.340
I'll pick you up later tonight.

20:16.370 --> 20:16.910
Okay.

20:16.930 --> 20:18.340
See you later.

20:23.380 --> 20:24.620
Tonight,

20:25.670 --> 20:26.310
are you going out to have fun?

20:26.330 --> 20:27.010
Yeah.

20:27.190 --> 20:28.190
Whether Lu Yan can stop being single

20:28.200 --> 20:29.470
depends on tonight.

20:30.870 --> 20:32.190
It's that important?

20:35.180 --> 20:36.010
Captain Jiang,

20:36.030 --> 20:37.300
thank you so much.

20:37.630 --> 20:38.940
I'll get going then.

20:39.120 --> 20:40.200
Go ahead.

20:49.380 --> 20:50.010
You look nice.

20:50.100 --> 20:51.230
Why aren't you wearing a skirt?

20:51.230 --> 20:52.230
Isn't this your date?

20:52.230 --> 20:53.530
You're the one who should wear the skirt.

20:54.040 --> 20:55.000
What?

20:55.070 --> 20:55.510
There he is.

21:00.920 --> 21:01.910
Is your date

21:01.950 --> 21:02.790
Wen?

21:03.880 --> 21:04.590
No.

21:04.610 --> 21:05.410
Then who is it?

21:05.430 --> 21:06.420
You'll know when we get there.

21:06.620 --> 21:07.540
Sorry for keeping you waiting.

21:08.640 --> 21:09.670
Thanks

21:09.670 --> 21:10.510
for coming all the way here.

21:10.670 --> 21:11.460
Don't mention it.

21:11.580 --> 21:12.630
It's cold—hurry up and get in the car.

21:12.630 --> 21:13.640
Hurry, get in.

21:31.180 --> 21:32.670
Leo...

21:38.300 --> 21:39.910
Leo...

21:40.950 --> 21:42.460
She doesn't like that one either.

21:43.260 --> 21:44.850
Nice shot!

21:45.550 --> 21:46.230
Nice shot!

21:46.300 --> 21:46.930
Impressive.

21:46.990 --> 21:47.540
Dad.

21:47.540 --> 21:48.950
Calm down. Be careful not to strain yourself.

21:55.620 --> 21:56.890
There are still a few.

21:59.390 --> 22:00.750
Rock climber...

22:03.710 --> 22:04.700
Rock climbing?

22:06.650 --> 22:07.540
Rock climbing—

22:08.300 --> 22:11.120
this suggests that the suspect

22:11.370 --> 22:13.230
has very good physical fitness.

22:13.480 --> 22:14.910
Maybe they're into sports.

22:20.470 --> 22:21.460
What cases are you all

22:22.000 --> 22:23.540
working on right now?

22:24.190 --> 22:25.160
Well,

22:27.040 --> 22:28.210
emotional disputes.

22:31.680 --> 22:33.340
You're even handling

22:33.390 --> 22:35.710
emotional disputes now?

22:37.510 --> 22:38.430
A crime of passion.

22:38.590 --> 22:39.540
A crime of passion.

22:42.530 --> 22:43.230
Let me tell you.

22:43.270 --> 22:45.300
Crimes of passion

22:45.910 --> 22:47.640
may seem simple on the surface,

22:47.670 --> 22:50.310
but the clues are actually quite complex.

22:50.390 --> 22:50.910
You understand, right?

22:50.910 --> 22:51.910
Goal, Dad.

22:51.910 --> 22:52.700
Goal.

22:56.830 --> 22:58.470
Let me tell you.

22:58.500 --> 23:00.990
I came across a crime of passion a few years ago.

23:01.010 --> 23:01.550
Dad.

23:01.580 --> 23:02.680
Stop it.

23:11.100 --> 23:14.400
[The Somekh Building]

23:16.270 --> 23:17.350
Hello, Mr. Wen.

23:23.280 --> 23:24.450
Such an impressive place.

23:26.110 --> 23:27.300
What is this?

23:32.060 --> 23:33.220
Hello, please come in.

23:42.260 --> 23:42.800
Let's go.

23:47.280 --> 23:47.970
Oh my!

23:48.280 --> 23:49.640
This place is really big.

23:51.350 --> 23:52.460
So much wine.

23:54.590 --> 23:55.230
Hurry up.

23:58.840 --> 24:00.140
Thank you, Wen.

24:03.990 --> 24:04.640
Wen.

24:04.780 --> 24:06.340
Your clubhouse is really beautiful.

24:06.390 --> 24:07.420
Did you design it yourself?

24:07.680 --> 24:08.290
No.

24:08.570 --> 24:09.440
I hired a designer

24:09.460 --> 24:10.650
from abroad to design it.

24:11.500 --> 24:12.480
Have a seat.

24:13.030 --> 24:13.660
No, thanks.

24:14.240 --> 24:15.530
I still have work calls to make.

24:15.960 --> 24:16.640
Please take a look at the menu first.

24:16.760 --> 24:17.160
Alright.

24:21.030 --> 24:22.410
Order whatever you like; don't be shy.

24:22.740 --> 24:23.230
Okay.

24:30.130 --> 24:30.750
Yan.

24:31.650 --> 24:33.450
This fried lamb chop

24:33.480 --> 24:34.520
costs 432 yuan.

24:33.600 --> 24:35.450
[Main Course Series]

24:34.540 --> 24:35.710
So expensive!

24:35.740 --> 24:37.540
Are you stupid? Look closely.

24:37.570 --> 24:39.220
This is the calorie count.

24:42.030 --> 24:44.100
They really have strict management for celebrities.

24:44.130 --> 24:44.910
Seeing the calorie count,

24:44.950 --> 24:45.890
I don't even want to eat it.

24:46.070 --> 24:47.110
You're not a celebrity.

24:47.230 --> 24:48.150
Just eat it.

24:48.170 --> 24:49.280
I'm going to the restroom.

24:50.100 --> 24:51.220
You're right.

25:03.890 --> 25:05.460
Can I join you for a meal?

25:06.390 --> 25:07.800
There's someone here.

25:07.890 --> 25:09.340
Would you like to share the table with us?

25:12.690 --> 25:13.290
You...

25:15.360 --> 25:17.040
Are you Yu Bofeng?

25:17.510 --> 25:18.250
Hello.

25:20.890 --> 25:21.880
Hello.

25:21.920 --> 25:24.110
This is the first time I've seen you in person.

25:24.270 --> 25:25.230
I really like you.

25:25.270 --> 25:25.940
Really.

25:29.130 --> 25:29.850
Can I sit down?

25:30.030 --> 25:30.550
Sure.

25:30.570 --> 25:31.410
Please have a seat.

25:33.270 --> 25:34.040
Oh my.

25:34.170 --> 25:35.700
I must be dreaming.

25:38.280 --> 25:39.180
Aren't you sitting down?

25:40.880 --> 25:41.870
I'll sit down.

25:42.680 --> 25:44.710
I heard from Mr. Wen

25:45.710 --> 25:47.000
that you're also my fan, right?

25:47.470 --> 25:48.130
Yes.

25:48.380 --> 25:49.860
Ever since I debuted...

25:51.460 --> 25:52.150
No.

25:52.250 --> 25:53.740
I've liked you

25:53.760 --> 25:55.090
since your debut.

25:55.120 --> 25:55.750
Really.

25:57.050 --> 25:57.730
Thank you.

25:57.820 --> 25:59.950
Your face looks so small in person.

26:00.850 --> 26:02.430
And you're really tall.

26:02.810 --> 26:04.560
Your skin is so fair.

26:06.320 --> 26:07.490
I also think you are beautiful.

26:09.470 --> 26:10.700
And I heard from Mr. Wen

26:10.750 --> 26:12.660
that your name is

26:14.740 --> 26:15.310
Wang...

26:17.470 --> 26:18.270
Qianqian.

26:19.680 --> 26:20.550
Yes!

26:20.580 --> 26:21.740
I'm Wang Qianqian.

26:21.760 --> 26:22.200
Yes.

26:22.410 --> 26:23.500
I didn't expect

26:23.520 --> 26:24.840
you to know my name.

26:24.870 --> 26:25.410
Of course I remember.

26:25.430 --> 26:25.910
Because I think

26:25.910 --> 26:26.790
this name sounds really nice.

26:26.810 --> 26:27.920
You two started chatting already?

26:29.180 --> 26:30.100
Are you happy?

26:30.210 --> 26:31.080
Yan...

26:31.110 --> 26:32.520
Did you arrange this for me?

26:32.540 --> 26:33.100
Yes.

26:33.120 --> 26:33.710
Oh my god.

26:33.740 --> 26:34.150
Quick,

26:34.180 --> 26:35.190
feel my heartbeat.

26:35.830 --> 26:36.840
Are you happy?

26:36.870 --> 26:37.510
I feel like

26:37.510 --> 26:38.070
I can't breathe anymore.

26:38.070 --> 26:38.510
Hello.

26:38.550 --> 26:38.950
Hello.

26:39.250 --> 26:39.750
Oh yeah.

26:39.750 --> 26:41.390
Mr. Wen just told me that

26:41.410 --> 26:42.610
he has a conference call to attend.

26:42.630 --> 26:43.540
He asked us not to wait for him

26:43.560 --> 26:44.390
and to eat first.

26:44.430 --> 26:45.650
He really went to a meeting.

26:45.670 --> 26:46.870
Are you going to eat with us?

26:46.900 --> 26:48.030
You have to eat too, right?

26:48.350 --> 26:48.990
I'm a human too,

26:49.010 --> 26:50.230
of course I have to eat.

27:07.660 --> 27:09.130
I've cut up my steak for you.

27:09.160 --> 27:10.370
You can have mine.

27:11.010 --> 27:11.990
Let's swap our portions.

27:17.670 --> 27:18.110
I...

27:21.200 --> 27:22.420
What's wrong? Why aren't you eating?

27:23.510 --> 27:23.910
You...

27:24.300 --> 27:25.320
Why are you staring at me?

27:25.780 --> 27:27.020
Or,

27:27.420 --> 27:28.030
is there anything else

27:28.030 --> 27:28.870
you need help with?

27:32.110 --> 27:32.710
No way.

27:32.710 --> 27:33.920
I need to go out and calm down.

27:35.580 --> 27:36.360
You...

27:41.840 --> 27:42.570
I'm full.

27:43.780 --> 27:44.430
You...

27:44.710 --> 27:45.730
You're done?

27:45.760 --> 27:47.160
I often skip dinner at night

27:47.260 --> 27:48.360
to stay in shape.

27:50.870 --> 27:51.590
It's fine. Tonight,

27:51.630 --> 27:52.550
I'm just really happy

27:52.550 --> 27:53.390
to be eating with you two.

27:58.530 --> 27:59.190
Should I

27:59.240 --> 27:59.830
cut your steak for you?

28:00.020 --> 28:00.840
No need.

28:01.190 --> 28:02.520
I'm more professional with the knife than you.

28:02.940 --> 28:03.850
Thank you for today.

28:04.950 --> 28:05.870
You're welcome.

28:08.390 --> 28:09.440
Lu Yan!

28:14.670 --> 28:15.790
Forget about how inappropriately

28:15.810 --> 28:16.750
you're dressed,

28:16.770 --> 28:18.480
but now you're meeting another man?

28:18.660 --> 28:19.290
I'm not...

28:19.320 --> 28:20.130
I'm not sick.

28:20.150 --> 28:21.030
You know that.

28:21.180 --> 28:22.350
You went with me to see the doctor.

28:22.370 --> 28:23.290
Don't you remember?

28:23.320 --> 28:24.250
Lu Yan!

28:26.180 --> 28:27.060
Lu Yan.

28:27.270 --> 28:28.250
It's you again.

28:28.490 --> 28:29.150
You corrupted

28:29.170 --> 28:30.250
my Qianqian.

28:30.270 --> 28:31.190
Look,

28:31.300 --> 28:33.630
I've been looking for her for so long.

28:34.710 --> 28:36.090
You stalked her?

28:36.150 --> 28:37.840
Do you know that's illegal?

28:38.020 --> 28:39.060
Illegal?

28:39.470 --> 28:40.670
She's mine.

28:40.690 --> 28:42.580
I can do whatever I want with her.

28:44.510 --> 28:45.220
Call the police.

28:45.260 --> 28:46.180
Call the police!

28:47.050 --> 28:47.770
Don't go.

28:48.730 --> 28:49.550
You came here

28:49.550 --> 28:50.730
to meet him, didn't you?

28:51.020 --> 28:52.190
You, don't go!

28:52.210 --> 28:53.370
What are you doing?

28:53.670 --> 28:54.470
Don't go!

28:56.950 --> 28:57.760
Lu Yan.

29:01.710 --> 29:03.380
Is it illegal now?

29:03.400 --> 29:04.380
I'll kill you.

29:05.030 --> 29:06.900
If you kill her, you won't survive either.

29:06.930 --> 29:07.960
Anyway, you don't want me anymore.

29:07.980 --> 29:08.640
Go away!

29:11.280 --> 29:12.580
Zhang Xiaohui!

29:13.640 --> 29:15.320
Put down the knife.

29:15.940 --> 29:17.300
I promise you that

29:17.320 --> 29:18.510
I will never break up with you.

29:18.550 --> 29:18.990
Okay?

29:19.010 --> 29:20.040
Do you think

29:20.060 --> 29:21.530
I still trust you guys now?

29:21.550 --> 29:22.960
Really. Trust me.

29:25.190 --> 29:26.730
I'm begging you, Zhang Xiaohui.

29:27.350 --> 29:28.630
Let Lu Yan go first,

29:28.630 --> 29:29.300
okay?

29:29.750 --> 29:31.440
I'll do whatever you say.

29:31.750 --> 29:32.590
I'll resign.

29:32.620 --> 29:33.290
I'll resign, okay?

29:33.310 --> 29:34.590
I'll stay at home with you.

29:34.630 --> 29:35.470
I'll quit everything

29:35.490 --> 29:36.590
and do whatever you say.

29:36.620 --> 29:37.930
Please let Lu Yan go, okay?

29:37.960 --> 29:40.450
They say women are cheap and shameless!

29:42.190 --> 29:42.910
Shut up!

29:43.250 --> 29:44.990
Qianqian and I will never be apart.

29:50.110 --> 29:50.910
Yan.

30:02.060 --> 30:03.200
Freeze! Police!

30:03.860 --> 30:04.520
Put down the knife!

30:07.520 --> 30:08.580
Don't move!

30:14.060 --> 30:14.830
Are you okay?

30:17.920 --> 30:18.750
Tell me

30:18.790 --> 30:19.270
what exactly happened.

30:21.800 --> 30:22.920
I'm the person in charge here.

30:23.250 --> 30:23.980
Let me explain it

30:24.020 --> 30:24.920
to you.

30:39.030 --> 30:41.110
The wound isn't deep,

30:41.390 --> 30:43.020
but make sure it stays dry

30:43.120 --> 30:43.960
and avoid stretching it.

30:46.510 --> 30:47.750
Thank you for today,

30:48.390 --> 30:48.910
Wen.

30:55.030 --> 30:55.670
Are you okay?

30:58.990 --> 30:59.740
After all,

30:59.760 --> 31:00.830
it's all my fault.

31:01.060 --> 31:01.630
If I hadn't

31:01.630 --> 31:02.790
asked you to come...

31:03.120 --> 31:04.670
We're the ones causing you trouble.

31:05.650 --> 31:06.900
I really didn't expect

31:07.190 --> 31:08.860
that he'd install a tracker in her phone.

31:09.030 --> 31:10.240
You see, he followed us all the way here.

31:11.260 --> 31:12.480
It's also my fault for not thinking things through.

31:12.680 --> 31:13.780
I can't believe such a thing happened

31:13.830 --> 31:14.910
in my clubhouse.

31:19.730 --> 31:20.950
Zhang Xiaohui

31:20.990 --> 31:22.000
has been arrested by the police,

31:22.260 --> 31:24.150
but we don't know how many days he'll be locked up.

31:24.310 --> 31:25.710
Maybe we should talk to Dr. Han,

31:26.360 --> 31:27.680
so you can study somewhere else

31:27.710 --> 31:28.590
for a while.

31:28.800 --> 31:29.640
No need.

31:29.990 --> 31:31.030
I can't avoid it.

31:31.510 --> 31:32.790
Qianqian and I will just be more careful.

31:34.840 --> 31:35.580
Yan.

31:37.390 --> 31:38.510
I've already explained everything clearly

31:38.550 --> 31:39.390
to the police.

31:41.590 --> 31:42.480
Wen,

31:42.500 --> 31:43.590
I'm really sorry

31:43.670 --> 31:44.550
for causing you trouble today.

31:45.130 --> 31:45.750
It's okay.

31:45.920 --> 31:46.720
As long as you're alright.

31:48.110 --> 31:48.610
Well...

31:48.720 --> 31:50.520
Yan, let's go home.

31:50.790 --> 31:51.740
I'll give you a ride.

31:51.890 --> 31:53.110
No need, Wen.

31:53.520 --> 31:54.620
I've called a taxi.

31:55.250 --> 31:56.170
We're leaving now.

31:56.350 --> 31:57.270
Remember, don't let it get wet.

31:57.300 --> 31:58.230
Don't lift heavy things.

31:59.920 --> 32:00.650
Are you okay?

32:00.980 --> 32:01.700
I'm fine.

32:10.680 --> 32:12.380
Check on Zhang Xiaohui for me.

32:12.980 --> 32:14.380
See if he has a criminal record.

32:15.080 --> 32:16.290
I want him in prison—

32:17.080 --> 32:18.700
the longer, the better.

32:19.250 --> 32:20.370
Yes, Mr. Wen.

32:24.830 --> 32:28.100
[Ninghai Anshan People's Hospital]

32:28.040 --> 32:29.690
Here, I brought coffee for everyone.

32:31.870 --> 32:32.510
Thank you, Mr. Wen.

32:32.540 --> 32:33.550
-Thank you, Mr. Wen.
-Thank you, Wen.

32:33.640 --> 32:34.390
Thank you, Mr. Wen.

32:34.410 --> 32:35.180
Thank you, Mr. Wen.

32:35.280 --> 32:36.750
You should visit Dr. Han more often.

32:36.790 --> 32:37.550
He always says he misses you.

32:37.180 --> 32:38.800
[Nurse Station]

32:37.740 --> 32:38.200
Yeah,

32:38.230 --> 32:38.870
I came this time

32:38.910 --> 32:39.630
just to see Dr. Han

32:39.630 --> 32:40.160
and everyone here.

32:40.180 --> 32:40.670
Is it good?

32:41.310 --> 32:41.980
Dr. Lu,

32:42.010 --> 32:43.640
Mr. Wen is treating everyone to coffee.

32:44.880 --> 32:45.620
Have you finished your work?

32:46.280 --> 32:47.070
This smells really good.

32:47.070 --> 32:48.870
How come you have time to come over today?

32:49.160 --> 32:49.890
Thank you.

32:51.150 --> 32:51.920
Have you eaten yet?

32:52.230 --> 32:53.510
Not yet, I'm about to go now.

32:54.150 --> 32:54.790
That's perfect.

32:54.810 --> 32:56.440
I can use your meal card

32:56.600 --> 32:57.690
since they've all finished eating.

32:58.200 --> 32:59.130
Sure, I'll just drop off my things.

32:59.220 --> 32:59.750
Okay.

33:05.740 --> 33:07.140
Does your hand still hurt?

33:07.980 --> 33:08.700
It doesn't hurt anymore.

33:08.730 --> 33:09.530
It's much better.

33:15.420 --> 33:16.520
I still really miss

33:16.540 --> 33:17.450
the smell of the hospital.

33:17.640 --> 33:18.350
Right?

33:20.510 --> 33:21.950
Did you sleep well last night?

33:22.500 --> 33:23.550
I was fine, actually.

33:23.570 --> 33:25.100
It's just that Qianqian was really scared.

33:25.440 --> 33:26.440
She needs to rest for a few days.

33:26.450 --> 33:27.360
I've helped her take leave.

33:29.090 --> 33:30.070
I've already asked someone

33:30.090 --> 33:31.740
to help her look for a new place.

33:32.030 --> 33:32.730
If they find one,

33:32.790 --> 33:33.830
just have her move in as soon as possible.

33:34.190 --> 33:35.440
Why trouble yourself with this?

33:35.470 --> 33:36.550
I'll handle it for her.

33:36.760 --> 33:37.890
I already feel guilty

33:37.920 --> 33:39.090
about what happened yesterday.

33:39.270 --> 33:40.520
Let me do something for her.

33:41.630 --> 33:42.230
Okay.

33:42.540 --> 33:45.310
But don't find her a place that's too expensive.

33:46.360 --> 33:47.750
Don't worry, I understand.

33:49.490 --> 33:50.220
By the way,

33:50.620 --> 33:51.870
I still have to thank you.

33:51.890 --> 33:53.230
Qianqian was so happy

33:53.260 --> 33:54.650
to see her Prince Charming yesterday.

33:54.750 --> 33:55.630
She was excited all night.

33:56.830 --> 33:57.670
You're talking about

33:57.710 --> 33:58.510
Yu Bofeng, right?

33:59.550 --> 34:00.080
Yes.

34:01.280 --> 34:02.500
Do you think he's handsome?

34:03.070 --> 34:04.430
I think he's

34:05.430 --> 34:06.330
okay,

34:06.620 --> 34:07.670
but he's not really

34:07.690 --> 34:08.650
my type.

34:10.940 --> 34:12.429
What's your type?

34:12.739 --> 34:13.880
I like them

34:13.949 --> 34:14.830
taller,

34:14.840 --> 34:16.050
more muscular—

34:16.080 --> 34:17.199
the manly type.

34:17.860 --> 34:19.850
It feels more comfortable being with them.

34:21.570 --> 34:23.429
So you're talking about Logger Vick, right?

34:23.550 --> 34:24.590
Logger Vick?

34:25.790 --> 34:26.480
Logger Vick

34:26.500 --> 34:27.469
is very responsible.

34:27.500 --> 34:29.130
Logger Vick is so funny.

34:29.489 --> 34:31.560
So who do you prefer, Briar or Bramble?

34:33.870 --> 34:35.199
I prefer Bramble.

34:35.230 --> 34:36.530
He seems a bit silly.

34:36.699 --> 34:38.340
The dishes today are really good.

34:38.489 --> 34:40.080
Here, have some braised pork.

34:40.110 --> 34:40.739
Alright.

34:40.980 --> 34:42.310
It looks good.

34:43.050 --> 34:43.850
How is it?

34:44.400 --> 34:44.900
Tasty.

34:44.929 --> 34:45.750
Is it tender?

34:46.150 --> 34:46.880
Not bad.

34:46.900 --> 34:47.750
Mom, try some.

34:53.230 --> 34:54.030
This.

34:54.060 --> 34:55.340
Can you guys eat outside?

35:02.820 --> 35:03.840
What's wrong?

35:06.650 --> 35:07.690
Are you craving our food now?

35:10.400 --> 35:12.000
I'll eat it so you can hear how amazing it is.

35:16.570 --> 35:18.590
This braised pork is incredible.

35:18.740 --> 35:20.270
The timing is absolutely perfect.

35:21.150 --> 35:23.450
The skin is soft, tender, and pleasantly chewy.

35:23.770 --> 35:25.400
The fatty meat practically melts in my mouth.

35:26.400 --> 35:27.840
The lean meat isn't dry either.

35:28.950 --> 35:30.270
It's salty and sweet, perfectly balanced.

35:30.940 --> 35:33.710
Clearly, the perfect dish for rice.

35:37.460 --> 35:39.300
Why is it so good?

35:40.450 --> 35:41.440
It's incredible with rice,

35:41.450 --> 35:42.780
and just as amazing on its own.

35:46.820 --> 35:47.690
What's going on?

35:53.550 --> 35:58.440
[Dr. Lu, your uncle is feeling a bit unwell. Can you come take a look?]

36:01.470 --> 36:03.050
[Lu Yan]

36:06.520 --> 36:07.100
Mom.

36:07.790 --> 36:08.450
Your phone.

36:16.030 --> 36:17.440
Hello, Dr. Lu.

36:17.710 --> 36:18.650
What's going on?

36:19.100 --> 36:20.600
Is Uncle not feeling well?

36:21.870 --> 36:23.020
Not feeling well?

36:23.300 --> 36:23.940
No...

36:29.790 --> 36:30.570
Yes.

36:31.890 --> 36:32.990
Your uncle

36:33.030 --> 36:34.590
is feeling a bit unwell.

36:37.640 --> 36:38.870
Can you tell me exactly

36:38.890 --> 36:39.860
where it hurts?

36:39.950 --> 36:41.640
Where exactly does it hurt?

36:42.310 --> 36:44.990
I... I can't really tell.

36:45.240 --> 36:46.560
It would be best if Dr. Lu

36:46.590 --> 36:47.610
could come by.

36:49.810 --> 36:50.900
That's great.

36:50.990 --> 36:51.790
Thank you.

36:51.790 --> 36:52.950
We'll wait for you.

36:53.480 --> 36:55.030
Who's not feeling well?

36:57.740 --> 36:59.260
Do you want to eat the food I made?

36:59.650 --> 37:00.790
If you do, then be quiet.

37:06.790 --> 37:07.910
Sorry, Wen.

37:07.910 --> 37:09.180
I need to go check on a patient.

37:09.210 --> 37:09.870
It's fine.

37:10.390 --> 37:11.000
Just leave it here.

37:11.020 --> 37:11.540
I'll take care of it.

37:11.820 --> 37:13.060
Okay, thank you.

37:28.610 --> 37:29.530
Auntie.

37:30.870 --> 37:31.830
Dr. Lu, you're here.

37:31.850 --> 37:32.410
Uncle.

37:32.440 --> 37:33.320
Where do you feel unwell?

37:33.670 --> 37:34.880
-My throat...
-His head hurts.

37:37.420 --> 37:38.020
He...

37:38.170 --> 37:39.680
He's unwell all over.

37:39.710 --> 37:41.080
Please take a look at him.

37:42.140 --> 37:42.910
Auntie,

37:42.950 --> 37:44.850
how about I call

37:44.880 --> 37:45.580
Uncle's attending physician over?

37:45.610 --> 37:46.540
No need.

37:46.560 --> 37:47.980
Just check on him yourself.

37:48.010 --> 37:49.100
Has his blood pressure been measured?

37:49.120 --> 37:50.420
It was checked this morning—normal.

37:50.450 --> 37:51.470
Let me test it again.

38:01.840 --> 38:03.010
It's a little high,

38:03.040 --> 38:04.290
but still within the normal range.

38:04.320 --> 38:05.250
It's high?

38:05.270 --> 38:06.220
Let me take a look.

38:10.960 --> 38:12.320
I asked Dr. Han this morning.

38:12.360 --> 38:13.510
If his blood pressure is normal,

38:13.550 --> 38:14.720
he can be discharged.

38:14.900 --> 38:15.920
I can be discharged?

38:15.940 --> 38:16.920
So soon?

38:16.990 --> 38:18.420
What's the rush?

38:18.630 --> 38:19.390
His blood pressure

38:19.410 --> 38:20.390
is high.

38:20.420 --> 38:21.790
What do you mean by "a little high"?

38:21.990 --> 38:22.560
Exactly.

38:22.950 --> 38:25.170
Besides, the wound on your neck hasn't healed yet.

38:25.190 --> 38:26.300
Don't let it get worse.

38:26.700 --> 38:27.760
Just stay for a few more days.

38:27.790 --> 38:29.800
That's right. Listen to your son.

38:40.350 --> 38:41.560
Dr. Lu.

38:41.830 --> 38:42.640
Well,

38:42.880 --> 38:44.630
I want to ask you something.

38:45.040 --> 38:45.660
I heard from

38:46.140 --> 38:47.230
one of the nurses

38:47.230 --> 38:48.710
at the nurse station

38:50.920 --> 38:52.490
that you went on a date yesterday.

38:54.080 --> 38:54.680
I...

38:54.950 --> 38:55.710
I...

38:56.470 --> 38:57.040
Yes.

38:57.320 --> 38:58.370
I went on a date.

39:00.470 --> 39:02.190
Was it with your boyfriend?

39:03.780 --> 39:05.010
What does he do for a living?

39:05.870 --> 39:07.800
You need to ask everything clearly.

39:07.830 --> 39:09.240
You need to know his background inside and out.

39:09.270 --> 39:10.570
There are so many bad people out there

39:10.630 --> 39:11.480
these days.

39:11.500 --> 39:12.360
You're such a pretty

39:12.390 --> 39:13.360
young woman;

39:13.390 --> 39:15.010
you must be careful, understand?

39:15.030 --> 39:16.560
What does his family do?

39:16.630 --> 39:17.950
You need to know the details.

39:18.030 --> 39:19.030
Don't just dive into

39:19.070 --> 39:20.460
a relationship recklessly,

39:20.490 --> 39:21.390
alright?

39:21.870 --> 39:23.270
You'd better find someone

39:23.310 --> 39:25.130
who works in the government, you know?

39:25.870 --> 39:27.030
Someone who's been through a background check.

39:51.100 --> 39:53.480
[Certificate of Honor]

39:58.710 --> 39:59.300
[Merit Student in the First Semester of the 2014-2015 Academic Year,
Recognized for Outstanding Academic Performance]

39:58.710 --> 39:59.300
[Jiang Chengyi]

39:59.470 --> 40:00.820
[Certificate of Honor] [First Prize]

40:01.060 --> 40:03.410
[Certificate of Honor] [Excellent Student Cadre]

40:41.640 --> 40:43.790
Today marks the first birthday

40:43.790 --> 40:45.070
I'm celebrating with Jiang Chengyi

40:45.110 --> 40:46.830
in 2015.

40:47.000 --> 40:48.950
Look at our birthday star.

40:52.520 --> 40:53.460
Let me make a wish first.

40:53.490 --> 40:54.140
Make a wish.

40:59.020 --> 40:59.680
Done.

40:59.710 --> 41:00.070
Done?

41:00.110 --> 41:00.810
What did you wish for?

41:01.390 --> 41:02.180
I can't tell you.

41:03.070 --> 41:03.760
Alright.

41:05.250 --> 41:06.990
Happy Birthday.

41:11.660 --> 41:12.530
Where's my gift?

41:13.580 --> 41:14.430
What gift?

41:14.850 --> 41:15.950
Didn't you prepare a gift?

41:17.230 --> 41:18.310
Isn't this...

41:19.710 --> 41:21.200
Where is my gift?

41:21.880 --> 41:22.830
What?

41:25.300 --> 41:27.090
Where's my gift?

41:30.240 --> 41:31.190
Now that's more like it.

41:32.480 --> 41:33.680
Where's my gift?

41:33.700 --> 41:34.580
I can't reach it.

41:35.530 --> 41:36.880
♫As the city flickers♫

41:38.150 --> 41:41.010
♫It's as gentle as wind wrapping around rain♫

41:42.290 --> 41:43.580
♫And you, who love to smile♫

41:44.600 --> 41:47.050
♫Always offer your happiness to me first♫

41:48.080 --> 41:50.420
♫The humor of time♫

41:51.920 --> 41:54.360
♫No one to blame for breaking the promise♫

41:55.430 --> 42:01.190
♫It's because we met too soon that we missed each other♫

42:00.310 --> 42:03.970
[Album]

42:02.570 --> 42:04.190
♫We're stranded at sunset♫

42:04.070 --> 42:08.590
[All Photos]

42:05.300 --> 42:08.160
♫My sunburnt face doesn't mean a word♫

42:09.450 --> 42:10.880
♫The stubborn me♫

42:12.110 --> 42:14.800
♫I always think of the far future♫

42:15.590 --> 42:17.660
♫I walk willfully♫

42:16.600 --> 42:17.260
Are you happy?

42:17.290 --> 42:17.800
Blow out the candles.

42:17.830 --> 42:18.460
Blow out the candles.

42:18.500 --> 42:19.810
One, two, three.

42:19.040 --> 42:21.950
♫Like a star revolving around♫

42:22.600 --> 42:23.910
♫I turn around♫

42:23.240 --> 42:25.400
Happy Birthday!

42:25.070 --> 42:28.570
♫But you're not behind me♫

42:30.240 --> 42:31.820
♫Losing you♫

42:31.970 --> 42:32.850
It's too little.

42:32.640 --> 42:34.820
♫It's so unreal♫

42:36.010 --> 42:37.440
♫I hurt my love♫

42:38.160 --> 42:39.100
♫But still hope to♫

42:39.850 --> 42:42.540
♫Start anew♫

42:43.740 --> 42:45.760
♫There's a certain kind of squander♫

42:46.700 --> 42:48.830
♫Where I'm late to know who loves me♫

42:47.940 --> 42:49.070
Senior.

42:50.390 --> 42:52.360
♫When you're not here♫

42:50.780 --> 42:52.870
Do you have a girlfriend?

42:53.160 --> 42:56.470
♫Life becomes aimless♫

42:55.190 --> 42:55.750
No.

42:57.330 --> 42:59.010
♫I miss you♫

43:00.090 --> 43:02.230
♫It's so real♫

43:03.320 --> 43:04.870
♫The person I trust♫

43:05.440 --> 43:06.550
♫Insists on separating♫

43:05.950 --> 43:06.790
Jiang Chengyi.

43:07.060 --> 43:09.990
♫Who can explain?♫

43:08.750 --> 43:09.750
I like you.

43:11.220 --> 43:13.140
♫I'm not afraid of your happiness♫

43:12.320 --> 43:13.600
Do you feel the same way?

43:14.190 --> 43:16.400
♫I'm afraid you'll forget me♫

43:17.230 --> 43:19.660
♫To feel my heartache♫

43:18.390 --> 43:20.190
Would you be my boyfriend?

43:20.640 --> 43:22.210
♫When I no longer have the best♫

43:23.260 --> 43:26.980
♫I miss you missing me♫

43:30.980 --> 43:32.870
Do you want to be my boyfriend or not?

43:33.000 --> 43:34.280
Come down first.

43:38.850 --> 43:40.160
♫When I walk the path you've walked♫

43:40.940 --> 43:43.890
♫Waiting to bump into you on the street♫

43:41.740 --> 43:43.260
If you do,

43:43.840 --> 43:44.960
wait for me at the finish line

43:45.390 --> 43:46.890
♫Like yesterday♫

43:45.720 --> 43:48.650
at the 3,000-meter finish line

43:47.790 --> 43:50.330
♫Our forever had no end♫

43:49.760 --> 43:50.770
during the sports day.

43:51.590 --> 43:52.560
♫I'm the stupid one♫

43:55.470 --> 43:57.870
♫You've already engraved yourself in my pulse♫

43:59.300 --> 44:05.030
♫I don't want you to disappear like a rainbow♫

44:12.660 --> 44:14.210
♫Losing you♫

44:15.320 --> 44:17.430
♫It's so unreal♫

44:18.370 --> 44:20.000
♫I hurt my love♫

44:20.340 --> 44:21.590
♫But still hope to♫

44:22.170 --> 44:25.170
♫Start anew♫

44:26.070 --> 44:28.280
♫There's a certain kind of squander♫

44:29.180 --> 44:31.310
♫Where I'm late to know who loves me♫

44:32.700 --> 44:35.400
♫Losing you♫

44:35.750 --> 44:39.420
♫Life becomes aimless♫

44:40.180 --> 44:41.840
♫My love♫

44:42.810 --> 44:45.030
♫Must be honest♫

44:46.380 --> 44:47.900
♫The person I trust♫

44:48.260 --> 44:49.450
♫You are most deserving♫

44:49.940 --> 44:53.000
♫Of good things♫

44:55.220 --> 44:55.920
Director Huo.

44:56.720 --> 44:57.540
Jiang.

44:57.770 --> 44:59.580
When do you plan to come back?

45:00.890 --> 45:01.570
Director Huo.

45:01.940 --> 45:02.900
You

45:03.350 --> 45:04.240
called my dad first,

45:04.270 --> 45:05.270
didn't you?

45:06.540 --> 45:08.100
You caught me.

45:08.280 --> 45:09.510
Of course, I had to check with

45:09.510 --> 45:10.510
my old friend first.

45:10.850 --> 45:12.460
I heard his surgery was a success,

45:12.480 --> 45:14.100
so I felt safe coming to urge you.

45:15.230 --> 45:15.830
The day after tomorrow

45:15.830 --> 45:17.470
will be your last day of leave.

45:17.590 --> 45:19.620
Have you finished handling everything?

45:21.340 --> 45:21.940
Yes,

45:22.820 --> 45:24.630
everything is mostly taken care of.

45:26.830 --> 45:27.710
Director Huo.

45:28.910 --> 45:29.940
As for

45:30.750 --> 45:31.870
the transfer order given to me earlier,

45:33.960 --> 45:35.120
I've made up my mind now.
